config NFC_ST21NFC
        tristate "STMicroelectronics ST21NFCD NFC driver"
        depends on I2C
        ---help---
          STMicroelectronics ST21NFCD core driver. It implements the chipset
          NCI logic and hooks into the NFC kernel APIs. Physical layers will
          register against it.

          Say N if unsure.

